title: My GF's Mom Has Got It Goin' On
description: Kouichi's been together with his new girlfriend for a couple months, but she's still not ready to have sex with him. His pent-up energy reaches a peak when her hot mom catches him alone and offers to take his virginity instead... Can he manage to stay faithful?
author: Kurosu Gatari
